{"tid":1577663,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[求救]屋企人俾人追數 唔知點算好","createTime":"2019-09-17T21:20:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-18T00:05:27.000Z","uid":308229,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"46345a5c0e5675ba75e059d53bfcad8a07499648","tid":1577663,"uid":308229,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T21:20:39.000Z","msg":"我老豆個同鄉借錢嘅時候寫咗我老豆做聯絡人，跟住啲收數佬就開始煩我老豆，打電話，寄信（入面有張天地銀行），最近重要俾人癡埋鐵閘，我老豆同啲收數佬講咗話唔熟，但係佢地都唔理，照煩<br />\n<br />\n我老母就幾乎日日都屌我老豆，話佢隨隨便便就俾啲資料人，搞到全家人都要煩，要同老豆離婚。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n啱啱訓教嘅時候俾啲看更拍門先知啲人又貼嘢，搞到我宜家極不安，有冇人知道我宜家可以點做"},{"pid":"18199b4219f23003821576e855bd73cf68008737","tid":1577663,"uid":308229,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T21:21:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b592b7afbc008320bf10203a575215c30f6f3d6","tid":1577663,"uid":308229,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T21:21:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc58e803baccebc2c6fa1b01c2767a2d12b5fd2a","tid":1577663,"uid":308229,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T21:22:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24a427e98f8ff159416cd714737cc4d5692e0023","tid":1577663,"uid":308229,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T21:22:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"061e6082d3e4feee384226d8c3664e12994a8bcf","tid":1577663,"uid":308229,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T21:25:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/dead.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3cd8d2fe7e9ab3b6d82dd0f028ac8f6bbcf5a43","tid":1577663,"uid":79793,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T21:26:29.000Z","msg":"唔洗驚 吹你唔脹"},{"pid":"9cc333d0aaf9